1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,222
Here in the "Shapes" panel are all the symmetrical shapes for Sintel
在这里的"Shapes"面板中既是所有的SINTEL对称表情

2
00:00:04,252 --> 00:00:08,314
we have 26 facial and 2 more for pupil dilation
现在有26个面部表情以及另外2个用于瞳孔变大变小的表情

3
00:00:19,066 --> 00:00:20,660
while working on facial shapes
当我们使用面部表情进行工作时

4
00:00:20,630 --> 00:00:23,198
I found that working with "Texture Solid" shading enabled
我发现最好工作在“Texture solid”阴影打开的模式下

5
00:00:23,238 --> 00:00:26,087
which is in the "Property" shelf under "Display"
这个模式可以在"Display"下的“Property”栏里找到

6
00:00:26,207 --> 00:00:28,263
made it much nicer to work with
打开它会让工作变的更爽

7
00:00:28,413 --> 00:00:30,841
it gave me feedback on how our textures moved
因为它反馈出我们的纹理是如何移动的

8
00:00:30,831 --> 00:00:33,779
and was close to what she looked like once rendered
而且这效果和最终渲染后的效果也很接近

9
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:43,508
once the jaw and eyelids are rigged and weighted
一旦下巴和眼皮儿被链接骨骼和加权

10
00:00:43,498 --> 00:00:45,895
the first thing I do is to open the jaw
我做的第一件事就是打开下巴

11
00:00:45,895 --> 00:00:49,114
check and clean up the geometry inside the mouth
检查和清除嘴里面的一些几何体

12
00:00:49,466 --> 00:00:50,438
after that
然后

13
00:00:50,448 --> 00:00:56,366
I start creating a series of isolated shapes in full symmetrical form using "X Mirror" tool
我开始创建一系列独立的表情，他们都是用X轴镜像工具来实现完全对称的

14
00:00:56,396 --> 00:00:57,710
I start with proportional editing
我先以比例调整开始

15
00:00:57,670 --> 00:01:02,985
and then move onto editing individual vertex for final polishing
然后下一步针对各独立的顶点做调整使其光滑

16
00:01:03,427 --> 00:01:05,112
I like to work in symmetry
我喜欢工作在对称模式下

17
00:01:05,072 --> 00:01:07,860
because it gives me the full effective in each shape
因为它可以给我看每个表情的最终效果

18
00:01:07,940 --> 00:01:08,983
in the next section
接下来呢

19
00:01:08,953 --> 00:01:12,624
you'll see how I break up the shapes to create a symmetry
你会看到我怎么分割表情去创建对称

20
00:01:25,542 --> 00:01:30,607
on frame 220 you will notice that the only shape that I include in the rig is the screen shape
在220帧时，你会注意到在链接中唯一存在一种的表情是屏幕表情（?不知道是什么）

21
00:01:30,687 --> 00:01:31,901
to create the shape
要创建这种表情

22
00:01:31,861 --> 00:01:36,454
I first placed the eyelid rig and then built my screen shape around it
我首先需放置眼皮的链接，然后围绕它为每一个面部表情

23
00:01:55,581 --> 00:01:56,443
for each shape
创建了屏幕表情

24
00:01:56,453 --> 00:01:59,4
I checked on three things which I call it Three Ms
我检查了3个东东，我叫他们3个大M

25
00:01:59,512 --> 00:02:00,947
first: "Motion"
第一个M：Motion（运动）

26
00:02:01,067 --> 00:02:05,891
I stare between default shape at all angles ensuring everything moves naturally
我盯着看每个表情从默认状态到各个角度时的动作以保证所有东西动作都很自然

27
00:02:06,172 --> 00:02:07,747
second: "Mixing"
第二个M：“Mixing”（混合）

28
00:02:07,877 --> 00:02:10,595
since the goals to create shapes that are mixable
我们创建表情的目的是：让他们可混在一起以表现正常

29
00:02:10,665 --> 00:02:13,393
I mixed what I'm currently working on with other shapes
那么我就必须要把我正在做的每一片表情都与别的相吻合及混合

30
00:02:13,373 --> 00:02:16,141
and that ensures that they blend well together
这样就能保证他们很好的混接起来。

31
00:02:16,573 --> 00:02:18,197
third: "Mouth Open"
第三个M：“Mouth Open”（张开嘴）

32
00:02:18,288 --> 00:02:19,321
for all mouth shapes
对于每个嘴的表情

33
00:02:19,291 --> 00:02:25,048
I open the jaw and make sure that each shape is smooth inside the mouth and against the teeth
我会打开下巴去确认是不是每个表情在嘴内部是平滑的，而且是贴着牙齿的

34
00:02:27,184 --> 00:02:29,280
the shapes might not look like much now
这些表情可能现在看起来不那么逼真

35
00:02:29,220 --> 00:02:31,978
and that's because they're meant to be combined together
这个嘛是因为他们将要并需要被合并起来

36
00:02:32,018 --> 00:02:38,989
this layering method allows animators more flexibility to build more complex facial expression
这种分层的方法允许动画作家们更有柔性的创建复杂的面部表达。
